            'prompt': 'In {{spacex_s1}}, find the disaggregated revenue table that shows revenue by type (Services vs Products) and by segment for Q1 2026. I need to understand: (1) Is the $380 million Products revenue included within the $2,148 million Consumer revenue or is it separate? (2) What is the Services revenue vs Products revenue breakdown for the Connectivity segment? (3) Show the complete revenue disaggregation table with all line items.'
